readme:
Service Usage

This service allows Visa Application processing systems to get the payment for Visas from SAP in a dynamic environment where pricing and structures of visas can change rapidly.

Service Behaviour

This service is a standard request response pattern that SAP provides to anyone processing visa application. Its critical in the lodgement of visas and in particular to the external facing applications.

Service Variants

NA

Service Dependencies

NA

Service Composition

NA

Service Flow

This service utilises SAP as the backend only.

Transformation

None.

Service State Management Decisions

None.
